WEBVTT

00:01.004 --> 00:03.001
This is it, Max.
The first private party

00:03.003 --> 00:05.407
we've booked
in our cupcake shop.

00:07.003 --> 00:08.707
What?
You said it was a private party,

00:08.709 --> 00:10.927
and this is a party
I  keep near my privates.

00:11.829 --> 00:13.529
Fine, but they can't
smell it on your breath,

00:13.931 --> 00:15.013
So eat a mint after.

00:15.265 --> 00:17.049
No need.
It's peppermint Schnapps,

00:17.051 --> 00:19.017
'cause I think ahead.

00:19.269 --> 00:22.104
I think this calls
for a "First party" dance.

00:22.106 --> 00:23.171
♪ First par-tay

00:23.173 --> 00:25.140
♪ who gonna have
a first par-tay? ♪

00:25.142 --> 00:26.892
♪ we gon' have
a first par-tay ♪

00:26.894 --> 00:28.677
That's the exact same dance
you did

00:28.679 --> 00:32.229
When the Humane Society sent you
free puppy address labels.

00:32.232 --> 00:34.182
♪ Address labels

00:34.284 --> 00:35.751
♪ Who got doggies
on an envelope? ♪

00:35.752 --> 00:37.820
♪ who got doggies
on an envelope? ♪

00:37.821 --> 00:39.822
♪ I need another sip
of this ♪

00:39.823 --> 00:42.124
♪ wish I had
something stronger ♪

00:42.125 --> 00:44.160
Max, I'm sorry.
I can't help it.

00:44.161 --> 00:46.262
I'm just so excited
my genius marketing ideas

00:46.263 --> 00:48.030
are finally
starting to pay off.

00:48.031 --> 00:51.333
[Children screaming]
Quiet! Quiet!

00:51.334 --> 00:54.637
Quiet! Quiet!

00:55.138 --> 00:56.705
If you aren't listening,

00:56.706 --> 00:59.942
Cupcake Max can't teach you
how to decorate.

01:02.078 --> 01:04.146
[Laughter]

01:04.147 --> 01:07.216
[Laughs]

01:07.217 --> 01:09.885
[Children laugh]

01:12.055 --> 01:13.489
[Children laugh]

01:14.290 --> 01:16.158
It's weird
how sex is so great,

01:16.159 --> 01:19.395
and yet,
it makes these.

01:19.396 --> 01:21.764
